A '''blob race''' was a contest of speed between protoplasmic, gelatinous [[Umgullian blob]]s through a course of obstacles&mdash;from fine mesh screens to a bed of nails. It was a major betting sport in [[Umgul City]] on the planet [[Umgul/Legends|Umgul]]. The syrupy masses, usually [[Color/Legends|grayish green]] but laced with bright hues, rolled, slithered, and oozed their way through. Cheating on the races was punishable by [[Death/Legends|death]].<ref name="Hnn" />

